{"type": "article", "id": 16097, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2015-10-15T06:15:26Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 9442, "name": "Georg Jensen"}, {"id": 17228, "name": "CRE8"}, {"id": 8874, "name": "Fujifilm"}, {"id": 1581, "name": "Chloe"}, {"id": 17229, "name": "Andrea Reggiani"}, {"id": 2819, "name": "Marc Newson"}, {"id": 17230, "name": "Davide Tuberga"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 8, "praise_count": 77, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000339GJ4Nz7S25dCQKRqa.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h3>\r\n\t银制茶具 by Marc Newson&amp; Georg Jensen\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t丹麦设计公司 Georg Jensen 邀请澳大利亚设计师 Marc Newson 为他们设计一套银制茶具，包括奶壶、糖罐、茶壶、咖啡壶和一个托盘。三种壶上都有一个拉长的巨大把手，像是从容器边缘延伸出来，托盘边缘和茶壶、咖啡壶底部包裹着藤条，增加了与接触物的摩擦，以保证安全。此外，茶壶盖上带有一个内置的拉门，以方便向容器里加水。这套 Newson 茶具需要花费 3 个月以上的时间手工制作，数量只有十个，以限量版的形式发售，印有“MN”的制作者标记。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606060038087N9xfI5Ri6s2a4gC.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.67359413\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003808Qdxa1fHbMUt6iKW8.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.63202934\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003809L8kEaOTYl9fVv4jG.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.72738386\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606060038092JNuhcnLCipsHbvG.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.69315403\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003809H8GE3uor2khlUySv.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.74449878\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606060038104PLyHlqhJS29URbs.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.68704156\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tS/VASI by Andrea Reggiani &amp; Davide Tuberga\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span>这一系列的花瓶都是 3D 打印的，设计师试图用现代技术来诠释传统。经过建模、打印的步骤之后，依然使用烧制和上釉的传统手法。花瓶呈现出漂亮的渐变色，可以做出扭曲的造型，细看时还保留了线性纹路，成为具有现代感的陶瓷花瓶。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003810DcYPEt58dQxvVBiw.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.6625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003811WuYl9Ro2TCqAnw3k.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.6625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003811DcO4QkBPXi0jLbl5.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.6625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606060038121BVTXx4P60zd3ELY.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.51059322\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003812qbV0IBvUgCy1hxfs.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.51059322\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tTIES 灯 by CRE8 social venture\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t这款像灯笼一样的灯是可拆的，分为吊在天花板下或放在桌上两种，来自荷兰 CRE8 social venture 里年轻的设计师。每一块都是胶合板做的，它们形状一样，可以像积木一样搭建起来，任意改变以适应空间大小。光线通过方块的缝隙里透出，有古典园林的神秘感。<a href=\"http://www.crowdyhouse.com/shop/ceiling-lamp-ties/\" target=\"_blank\"> 这里是购买链接。</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003813vzBIi8octRUNq9Ew.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003813JezYKIRd0Qq3OXG6.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66702128\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606060038142hzLdgpHrUM9B8CZ.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66702128\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003814elDPCy5nzg0TE386.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75555556\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tSweet Sensing 温度计 by Hong-LinChen &amp; Hao-Cheng Fang\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t冰冷的温度计常常让儿童感到害怕，几乎成为疾病的预示。而这根数字温度计贴在身上时不会造成太多感觉，它除了能直接看到温度外，还能连上手机 app 以读取最新的体温，直接对温度变化做一个详见的记录。对正在发烧的儿童来说非常实用。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606060038155jsHdDtEkhzCGAJ8.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.48761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003815nw9j1dlQi4fqKMu8.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.55099895\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003816gdi4M9th7Esjl1mB.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.83428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003816N8zXWrCEOBGIH75i.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.69798658\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003816fazhKiJMH9GNtBPe.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.02310231\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tFujifilm Instax Wide by Fujifilm \r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t这是富士推出的新系列，比 Fujifilm Instax Mini 大两倍， 配备 90mm 的镜头和 3 种拍摄模式：Auto、长曝及 1/30 秒固定快门模式，其他功能都保留经典配置。例外在镜头盖，通常没有用的镜头盖在这里变成了快门遥控，手动下拉是非常原始传统的体验。即日将在网上预售，其中蓝绿配色为经典款。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003817btXGVcYRFerkBojJ.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003817SQvERq18VGakri4Y.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606060038182oP1CMQjNIEfVTSU.gif\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"gif\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606060038184KCOBLSrv6VlIFk8.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003819hwmYkb4Dp1M0BneU.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tChloé 春夏系列\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t这是刚刚结束的巴黎時裝秀里，Chloé（珂洛艾伊）发布的 2016 春夏系列。方形的皮包配上金属圆圈勾环似乎是它们的共同点，呈现像信封一样的复古感。有些包在圆环下坠着长流苏，随风摆动，让这一系列多了一份活泼灵动。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606060038199yZTEDcpLvgl40uM.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003820OANjyxTYd19hJZSQ.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003820SG5HqQZlCcBAN0b7.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003821LT6lsdRbChDfSrvq.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003821g4tzCdx9r8TmPDXR.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606060038229D7SiIyEkU4d2jOp.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}